bio: Alice Anderson is a compassionate LPC with years of experience helping individuals navigate life's challenges.
Bob Brown specializes in family dynamics and offers in-person sessions to support healthy relationships.
Catherine Clark is an LCSW providing virtual therapy, specializing in mental health and well-being.
Dr. David Davis, a licensed psychologist, brings expertise in cognitive-behavioral therapy to support clients in their mental health journey.
Dr. Elena Evans, a board-certified psychiatrist, offers comprehensive mental health care, including medication management.
Frank Fisher, LPCC, focuses on empowering individuals through evidence-based counseling techniques.
Gina Green is a CADC dedicated to helping individuals overcome substance abuse and addiction.
Henry Harris, MSW, is a skilled social worker providing support and advocacy for diverse communities.
Ivy Ingram, LSW, offers compassionate social work services, addressing the unique needs of each client.
James Johnson combines clinical expertise with a warm approach, supporting clients on their mental health journey.
